---

<section
  class="pt-32 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 via-white to-purple-50 dark:from-gray-900 dark:via-gray-800 dark:to-gray-900"
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <!-- Hero Headline -->
      <style>
        .headline-row {
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          justify-content: center;
          width: 100%;
          margin-bottom: 0.05em;
          flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
          .headline-row {
            flex-direction: column;
            text-align: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
          }
        }
        .headline-row:last-child {
          margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .fixed-text {
          text-align: right;
          white-space: nowrap;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
          .fixed-text {
            text-align: center;
          }
        }
        .changing-container {
          width: min(300px, 100%);
          text-align: left;
          margin-left: 1rem;
          min-height: 1.2em;
          position: relative;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
          .changing-container {
            margin-left: 0;
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
          }
        }
        .changing-business {
          position: relative;
          display: block;
          width: 100%;
          text-align: left;
          height: 1.2em;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
          .changing-business {
            text-align: center;
          }
        }
        .changing-business::after {
          content: "Restaurante";
          animation: changeWord 34s infinite;
          color: white;
          font-weight: bold;
          position: absolute;
          left: 50%;
          top: 0.1em;
          white-space: nowrap;
          transform: translateX(-50%);
        }
        @media (min-width: 769px) {
          .changing-business::after {
            left: 0;
            transform: none;
          }
        }

        @keyframes changeWord {
          0%, 5.88% { content: "Buffet"; }
          5.89%, 11.76% { content: "Cocktelería"; }
          11.77%, 17.64% { content: "Cafetería"; }
          17.65%, 23.52% { content: "Restaurante"; }
          23.53%, 29.41% { content: "Catering"; }
          29.42%, 35.29% { content: "Cervecería"; }
          35.30%, 41.17% { content: "Foodtruck"; }
          41.18%, 47.05% { content: "Chiringuito"; }
          47.06%, 52.94% { content: "Cocktelería"; }
          52.95%, 58.82% { content: "Churrería"; }
          58.83%, 64.70% { content: "Restaurante"; }
          64.71%, 70.58% { content: "Heladería"; }
          70.59%, 76.47% { content: "Foodtruck"; }
          76.48%, 82.35% { content: "Panadería"; }
          82.36%, 88.23% { content: "Pastelería"; }
          88.24%, 94.11% { content: "Pizzería"; }
          94.12%, 100% { content: "Sidrería"; }
        }
      </style>
      <h1
        class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-12 leading-tight flex flex-col gap-4 md:gap-2"
      >
        <div class="headline-row">
          <div class="fixed-text">
            <span class="text-gray-800 dark:text-white">Gestiona tu</span>
          </div>
          <div class="changing-container">
            <span class="changing-business dark:text-white"></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="headline-row">
          <span class="text-gray-800 dark:text-white">con</span>
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent ml-2 py-3">
            Inteligencia Artificial
          </span>
        </div>
      </h1>

      <!-- Hero Subtitle -->
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        Maingoo (r)evoluciona la gestión con automatización inteligente de facturas, 
        inventario y análisis de datos para optimizar tu negocio.
      </p>

      <!-- CTA Buttons -->
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mb-12">
        <a href="#contact" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:shadow-xl transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1 inline-block text-center">
          Solicitar Acceso a la Beta
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Hero Stats -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
  <div class="text-center">
    <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 mb-2 flex justify-center">
      <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Ahorra horas de trabajo cada semana</div>
  </div>
  <div class="text-center">
    <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 mb-2 flex justify-center">
      <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Facturas volcadas automáticamente con IA</div>
  </div>
  <div class="text-center">
    <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 mb-2 flex justify-center">
      <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20 7l-8-4-8 4m16 0l-8 4m8-4v10l-8 4m0-10L4 7m8 4v10M4 7v10l8 4"></path>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Inventario conectado en tiempo real</div>
  </div>
  <div class="text-center">
    <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 mb-2 flex justify-center">
      <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Datos seguros en la nube</div>
  </div>
  <div class="text-center">
    <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400 mb-2 flex justify-center">
      <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Plataforma escalable y modular</div>
  </div>
  <div class="text-center">
    <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-pink-600 dark:text-pink-400 mb-2 flex justify-center">
      <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Diseñado junto a gerentes reales</div>
  </div>
</div>


  </div>
</section>
